data.description: Update: New Carpet November 2023!!! Welcome to this gorgeous home in Tuscany Crossing sitting on a Cul De Sac lot. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and over 1600 sqft. The master bedroom has tiered ceilings and an en suite bathroom featuring a whirlpool tub and stall shower. The large kitchen has granite countertops and a tile backsplash. The backyard has a covered patio & extended patio area with a grill and firepit to stay with the home. Roof done in 2020. Also home is within walking distance to Haughton Middle School & within 15 minutes of BAFB.
